An Act relative to disclosure notice in the right to repair motor vehicle data law.
Be it enacted by the Senate and House of Representatives in General Court assembled, and by the authority
of the same, as follows:
1 Section 2 of Chapter 93K of the General Laws, as most recently amended by Section 4 of
2 Chapter 386 of the Acts of 2022, is hereby amended by striking subsections (g) and (h) and
3 inserting in place thereof the following subsection (g):-
4 (g) The Attorney General is hereby directed to establish a motor vehicle telematics
5 system notice which a vehicle manufacturer shall include in the owner’s manual provided for its
6 new motor vehicles beginning with model year 2026 vehicles and which shall include the
7 following information: (i) an explanation of motor vehicle telematics and its purposes; (ii) a
8 description summarizing the mechanical data collected, stored, and transmitted by a telematics
9 system; (iii) the prospective owner’s ability to access the vehicle’s mechanical data through a
